{"tid":102820,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"（2017年2月上旬）恭祝各位雞年心想事成！早上天氣稍涼，旬中有幾陣雨","createTime":"2017-02-01T01:02:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-10T17:52:02.000Z","uid":38255,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e84c60cfd975eb31e1ee04e07c4301b20535795d","tid":102820,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T01:02:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: navy;\"><strong><img src=\"http://x.co/wk017\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2Fwk017&h=0677eeb4&s={SIZE}\" /> <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">氣象討論：2017年2月上旬</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">此帖文討論期：2017年2月1日至10日</span></strong></span><br />\n【註】 氣象討論帖一般逢每月1日、11日及21日發出新帖文。　當新帖文發出後，或有颱風追擊帖發出，原有的氣象討論帖會隨即停用。　為使大家有一個良好舒適的瀏覽環境，請不要使用簡體中文貼文、提及力場或洗版，謝謝合作。　請勿直接張貼會自動更新的氣象圖片，請把圖片上傳至儲存空間後再轉貼在帖文上。謝謝。　以下圖片會自動更新。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">&lt;ins&gt;◤溫度術語&lt;/ins&gt;</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\">嚴寒 　　　　　≦ 7 &deg;C</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">寒冷 　 　　　8 - 12 &deg;C</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">清涼　　　　13 - 17 &deg;C</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">和暖／稍涼　18 - 22 &deg;C</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">溫暖　　　　23 - 27 &deg;C</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">炎熱　　　　28 - 32 &deg;C</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\">酷熱 　　 　　≧ 33 &deg;C</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">&lt;ins&gt;◤參考網頁&lt;/ins&gt;</span></span><br />\n◆ 認識天氣現象：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/education/edu01met_c.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Feducation%2Fedu01met_c.htm&d=xc0devjmTjk1MRQhR5SRZ26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=9d87943e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/education/edu01met_c.htm</a><br />\n◆ 各類天氣術語：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/currwx/flw_description/flw_c.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fwxinfo%2Fcurrwx%2Fflw_description%2Fflw_c.htm&d=xc0devjmTjk1MRQhR5SRZ26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=de4619dd\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/currwx/flw_description/flw_c.htm</a><br />\n◆ 各類警告定義：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/textonly/explain/introc.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Ftextonly%2Fexplain%2Fintroc.htm&d=xc0devjmTjk1MRQhR5SRZ26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=2c738228\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/textonly/explain/introc.htm</a><br />\n◆ 短期氣候預測：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/season/seasonc.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fwxinfo%2Fseason%2Fseasonc.htm&d=xc0devjmTjk1MRQhR5SRZ26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=1f8fabcd\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/season/seasonc.htm</a><br />\n◆ 香港天文台電腦預測：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/nhm/nhm_uc.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fnhm%2Fnhm_uc.htm&d=xc0devjmTjk1MRQhR5SRZ26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=de6f90d4\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/nhm/nhm_uc.htm</a><br />\n◆ ECMWF數值預報：<a href=\"http://x.co/ECMWF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2FECMWF&d=xc0devjmTjk1MRQhR5SRZ26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=baffbaa3\" target=\"_blank\">http://x.co/ECMWF</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏</span><br />\n<img src=\"http://j.mp/SuV1UB\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2FSuV1UB&h=aa5b9639&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://j.mp/1mOf5kb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2F1mOf5kb&h=f43ed746&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 地面天氣圖<br />\n<img src=\"http://j.mp/2a5ticH\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2F2a5ticH&h=b05f53f9&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://j.mp/2ahInaZ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2F2ahInaZ&h=2a1d8db0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://j.mp/2ajChbn\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2F2ajChbn&h=22f823b8&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://j.mp/2ap2lTE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2F2ap2lTE&h=475ff2cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 衛星雲圖<br />\n<img src=\"http://j.mp/2a7TpCM\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2F2a7TpCM&h=ef01e17d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://x.co/1Oc5V\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2F1Oc5V&h=2e7774ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://j.mp/Meu94L\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2FMeu94L&h=e469b653&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://j.mp/pSSahs\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fj.mp%2FpSSahs&h=61ae872d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲ 熱帶系統分佈</strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">&lt;ins&gt;氣象台專頁正式登場&lt;/ins&gt;</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong>我們自2008年起發表氣象帖。現在，一個屬於巴打絲打們的天氣專頁正式登場！我們以淺白易明的方式介紹氣象，讓您享受認識氣象箇中的樂趣。氣象不再沉悶空泛。<br />\n本專頁旨在為大家提供氣象相關的資訊，其中包括一些氣象小資料、即時的天氣及風暴等消息。設立的主要目的，是為了讓比較忙碌的巴打絲打們，即使沒時間或沒留意到高登氣象帖，都可透過另一個渠道獲得我們的氣象資訊。<br />\n[i]<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">請巴打絲打們到專頁讚好以示對我們支持及鼓勵</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"http://x.co/FBlike\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2FFBlike&h=5fdd3157&s={SIZE}\" /><a href=\"http://fb.com/HKGweather\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2FHKGweather&d=xc0devjmTjk1MRQhR5SRZ26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=951a1ccd\" target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/HKGweather</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://x.co/TWlike\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2FTWlike&h=e9b064ef&s={SIZE}\" /><a href=\"http://twitter.com/HKGweather\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHKGweather&d=xc0devjmTjk1MRQhR5SRZ26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=8128e654\" target=\"_blank\">http://twitter.com/HKGweather</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://x.co/UTube\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2FUTube&h=a22db7c9&s={SIZE}\" /><a href=\"http://youtube.com/HKGweather\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2FHKGweather&d=xc0devjmTjk1MRQhR5SRZ26tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=2ed9e6c3\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtube.com/HKGweather</a>/[i]</strong>"},{"pid":"9d419c08b827e3fa10549630d28aac4c745c7f19","tid":102820,"uid":34037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T01:13:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24382dfcb78b44005ec3ddbbf5fcf8e38d2cd168","tid":102820,"uid":42440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T01:25:10.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"96d22d09b12101253b6bd01a28f6b6aca57f9f38","tid":102820,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T04:18:27.000Z","msg":"SZMB : 30天氣候預測<br />\n預計月內天氣總體較平穩，氣溫波動較小，2月起轉多雨霧的天氣。月內最低氣溫在10℃及以下的寒冷天氣2-3天，較同期 月中旬，最低氣溫8-9℃左右。冷空氣大致出現在1月21-23日，2月2-3日，16-17日，其中2月份的冷空氣過程均伴有階段陰雨天氣。<br />\n春節假期（1月27日 - 2月2日），我市天氣整體較平穩，平均氣溫16-17℃，最低氣溫12-13℃左右，春節假期後期有1天左右的小雨。"},{"pid":"50456efb5b78b2623e1354f79f2917bb219268f0","tid":102820,"uid":44630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T00:11:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cf3458e72e7b46169c92acbfae425ef368b722b","tid":102820,"uid":39375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T09:29:20.000Z","msg":"推過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0292621fa82a8e932ba5196db3d789d11ef64dd5","tid":102820,"uid":17427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T10:48:00.000Z","msg":"今日體感好凍 完全唔似16 19"},{"pid":"30d9b55d9e1a31eb71c774c221cd175f4afdb9dc","tid":102820,"uid":22609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T10:55:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今日體感好凍 完全唔似16 19</blockquote><br />\nagger"},{"pid":"5733ac15588d4c8f6f5739c6c101f9f5c878fcea","tid":102820,"uid":39375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T13:30:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>今日體感好凍 完全唔似16 19</blockquote><br />\nagger</blockquote><br />\n我覺得感覺比實際低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ddf1273cc4becbfcef9cf7169e68689c2f79d8e","tid":102820,"uid":44630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T14:06:22.000Z","msg":"由於沒有顯著的寒潮影響廣東沿岸地區，<span style=\"color: red;\">二零一七年一月是有記錄以來最溫暖的一月，平均氣溫及平均最低氣溫分別為破紀錄的18.5度及17.0度，分別較正常數值高2.2度及2.5度。</span>本月亦較正常少雨。本月只錄得7.8毫米雨量，少於正常數值24.7毫米的三分之一。<br />\n    受一股偏東海洋氣流影響，本港於本月首五天天氣和暖，期間既有陽光亦有多雲的天氣。一月六日轉為普遍天晴，隨後兩天陽光充沛，香港天文台於一月八日的氣溫上升至最高的25.5度，是本月的最高氣溫。當晚一股東北季候風的補充抵達本港，隨後兩天較為多雲及稍涼。<br />\n    隨著一股偏東氣流逐漸增強及與南海一個低壓區相關的雲帶移向廣東沿岸地區，本港於一月十一日多雲及有薄霧。當東北季候風的補充抵達華南沿岸地區，一月十二日至十六日轉為密雲，天氣逐漸轉涼及有幾陣雨。隨著東北季候風逐漸緩和，其後天氣再度回暖，而本港附近的雲層亦於一月十九日開始消散，天氣轉為大致天晴。<br />\n    隨著一股顯著的東北季候風補充抵達本港，源於內陸的偏北風於一月二十日至二十二日為本港帶來乾燥及較涼的天氣。在雲量稀少的情況下，香港天文台於一月二十二日早上的氣溫降至最低的13.6度，為本月的最低氣溫。而周末期間陽光充沛，日間相對濕度降至百分之40以下，沙田小瀝源有山火報告。雖然一股偏東氣流於一月二十四日增強，本港於一月二十三日至二十七日持續天晴。受一股潮濕的偏東氣流影響，一月二十八日轉為多雲，農曆新年假期有幾陣雨及部分地區能見度頗低。隨著一股清勁至強風程度的偏東氣流於一月三十日晚上為華南沿岸地區帶來一股東北季候風的補充，本港天氣於月尾顯著轉涼。<br />\n<br />\n    本月有一個熱帶氣旋影響南海及北太平洋西部。"},{"pid":"f5312c6d7abc9fa99ca985a42e698936d1d0201f","tid":102820,"uid":45439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T14:23:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今日體感好凍 完全唔似16 19</blockquote><br />\n唔覺，我覺得涼得黎隻手好慶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />行耐左成身都滾滾地"},{"pid":"ce026debadd97ce02b4e5086c89ba150ccbcdaf7","tid":102820,"uid":41821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T01:23:04.000Z","msg":"聽日又落雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c25d42a994701a46b9a9051cbf104d047e1ade85","tid":102820,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T04:00:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽日又落雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實今個冬天好少雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bc7b5f65b4edd0a29e7aea01486d1f108db4ff5","tid":102820,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T04:48:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ynx0d36s\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fynx0d36s&h=daed3752&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能係入春前最後寒冷機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28a933455f05af1b2d19b07d563c210675c069b2","tid":102820,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T07:56:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/cbqv5k3d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fcbqv5k3d&h=af88be6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nno one cares<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過可以睇下有無幫助，<br />\n下星期扯多d冷空氣南下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"582a00f1b5ac41beba7354516270e9bbbc3f4d25","tid":102820,"uid":37210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-03T18:45:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b34cea7da13f9b2531c909cf177320721af49a0a","tid":102820,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T07:23:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/kfcomv3d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thu