f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係有一日著左U記羽"},{"pid":"085e3acb35a3380e5188fffa5d2835381d80c892","tid":102820,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T12:40:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/a0byqxT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fa0byqxT.jpg&h=47152fec&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n又摩西分紅海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但唔係分畀香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/6gdh5kqn\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F6gdh5kqn&h=82a0cb25&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5a0acb97307c4caa664a3934b2039009f99a467e","tid":102820,"uid":45439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T15:17:24.000Z","msg":"唔知係咪落雨關係，香港濕冷18度宇宙級全世界最凍，體感溫度低30度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cdc166271828bb061c0c0abed7b8d1f2f2259bd","tid":102820,"uid":68457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:31:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知係咪落雨關係，香港濕冷18度宇宙級全世界最凍，體感溫度低30度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n全球最凍的18度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef954622f5a7f7ba4d2bb46ac5937e3da5571396","tid":102820,"uid":45439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T16:45:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔知係咪落雨關係，香港濕冷18度宇宙級全世界最凍，體感溫度低30度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n全球最凍的18度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家17啦，真係凍過日本落雨幾度個隻，好怪但唔知點解"},{"pid":"76bb172ee58ef7741906ba92a3c1720f4084866e","tid":102820,"uid":9800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T07:48:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">空氣污染注意報</span><br />\n<br />\n現時全港吹微風，不利污染物吹散。<br />\n<br />\n健康忠告<br />\n<br />\n不適宜通風，請緊閉門窗<br />\n空氣嚴重污染，非常不適合開窗通風，請緊閉門窗。如果開窗會對老人與兒童，體弱者、呼吸道與心肺疾病患者的健康有嚴重影響<br />\n<br />\n建議佩戴口罩<br />\n空氣質量較差，出行時建議佩戴口罩，特別是老人與兒童，體弱者或心臟病、呼吸系統疾病患者。<br />\n<br />\n請勿進行戶外運動<br />\n敏感人群、心臟病和肺病患者的症狀顯著加劇，應當留在室內避免體力消耗。健康人群會普遍出現不適症狀、應當避免戶外運動，防止空氣污染對身體的損傷。"},{"pid":"983e78b8ac35772641e00152069600005550728f","tid":102820,"uid":70448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T08:53:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>成個冬天冇拎過大褸出黎著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係有一日著左U記羽</blockquote><br />\n舊年買嘅羽絨褸都無著到<br />\n今年唔心息，新年著件薄衫點都攞出嚟著一著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a728a55886b2d8fb178b5bb13fd77db7c9275418","tid":102820,"uid":9800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T09:35:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: orange;\">空氣污染注意報</span><br />\n<br />\n現時全港吹微風，不利污染物吹散。<br />\n<br />\n健康忠告<br />\n<br />\n不適宜通風，請緊閉門窗<br />\n空氣嚴重污染，非常不適合開窗通風，請緊閉門窗。如果開窗會對老人與兒童，體弱者、呼吸道與心肺疾病患者的健康有嚴重影響<br />\n<br />\n建議佩戴口罩<br />\n空氣質量較差，出行時建議佩戴口罩，特別是老人與兒童，體弱者或心臟病、呼吸系統疾病患者。<br />\n<br />\n請勿進行戶外運動<br />\n敏感人群、心臟病和肺病患者的症狀顯著加劇，應當留在室內避免體力消耗。健康人群會普遍出現不適症狀、應當避免戶外運動，防止空氣污染對身體的損傷。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/e2mRNhE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fe2mRNhE.png&h=11782031&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n從反軌跡路線圖中可見，氣團在香港附近綬慢移動，令空氣變差。"},{"pid":"82ff369bcd3628798e6ca087482c8bbaded68166","tid":102820,"uid":36046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:19:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>唔知係咪落雨關係，香港濕冷18度宇宙級全世界最凍，體感溫度低30度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n全球最凍的18度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家17啦，真係凍過日本落雨幾度個隻，好怪但唔知點解</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n日本幾度點都凍啲 係咪你喺日本著得多衫咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a1c7ed9c2e3c4a9c7dd51b41bb3ab9b0692d3e1","tid":102820,"uid":45439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:51:26.000Z","msg":"今晚又係宇宙級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"341bbe4a9d83a3e115bddc2ef4f76ac002449d28","tid":102820,"uid":44630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T15:19:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今晚又係宇宙級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n熱？"},{"pid":"d537b81ef2172552c8c76e02d83e5749479c801f","tid":102820,"uid":45439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T15:21:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>今晚又係宇宙級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n熱？</blockquote><br />\n係暖左"},{"pid":"dab890c4bf3f4db3bd8bb982e4c78236dafb0918","tid":102820,"uid":9800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T05:19:13.000Z","msg":"2月10/11日 最低氣溫下調至12度"},{"pid":"a5dffb24ab31717497f7e1db4c7f37d374ce3646","tid":102820,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T08:33:57.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">強烈季候風信號</span></span><br />\n<br />\n強烈季候風信號現正生效。預料本港吹偏東強風，平均風速每小時超過四十公里。陣風間中達烈風程度。<br />\n<br />\n1. 如果你身在當風地方，會受到偏東風的正面吹襲，請採取預防措施，以防強勁陣風帶來損害。花盆及可能被風吹倒的物件應搬入室內。<br />\n<br />\n2. 打算參加水上運動或進行海上工作人士請特別小心，以防大風大浪帶來的危險。在離岸海域，風浪尤其大。<br />\n<br />\n以上天氣稿由天文台於2017年02月06日16時15分發出</strong>"},{"pid":"6e7ff766d51c92abfff314ce6c7e7099a4ddd23c","tid":102820,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T08:44:56.000Z","msg":"菲東98w 取消gw<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60f90b969722d6bffddf55922c6cce248efd13d6","tid":102820,"uid":44630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T12:09:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>菲東98w 取消gw<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n等下啦 時辰未到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcec3945054f38d91c181ab70959f90f1803eb6f","tid":102820,"uid":9800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T15:26:17.000Z","msg":"污染物正沿海邊從東面襲港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3d7cc1cf066a1667eb28bf81b0d7561774aa141","tid":102820,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T15:32:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>菲東98w 取消gw<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n等下啦 時辰未到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無人care佢成唔成到風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34dd1b21e0ecfe9d79bd0fbf6fd5467f658cec6d","tid":102820,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T17:55:31.000Z","msg":"07/02/2017 01:30 十分鐘風向及風力（公里/小時）青洲 東北&nbsp;71<br />\n橫瀾島 東北偏東&nbsp;62<br />\n大老山 東&nbsp;61<br />\n香港航海學校 東北偏東&nbsp;45<br />\n長洲泳灘 東北偏東&nbsp;42<br />\n沙洲 東 40<br />\n赤柱 東 37<br />\n<br />\n現時風速相當強勁，<br />\n青洲達烈風程度，<br />\n橫瀾島亦一步之遙 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41ff2592316a1fd18833c01c022a79e926dd8652","tid":102820,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T17:56:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>07/02/2017 01:30<br />\n 十分鐘風向及風力（公里/小時）<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">青洲 東北&nbsp;71<br />\n橫瀾島 東北偏東&nbsp;62</span><br />\n大老山 東&nbsp;61<br />\n香港航海學校 東北偏東&nbsp;45<br />\n長洲泳灘 東北偏東&nbsp;42<br />\n沙洲 東 40<br />\n赤柱 東 37</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n現時風速相當強勁，<br />\n青洲達烈風程度，<br />\n橫瀾島亦一步之遙 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22e679d846ef36c560625afc25cdd8ca4612e1a9","tid":102820,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T18:03:13.000Z","msg":"07/02/2017 01:50<br />\n 一小時最高陣風（公里/小時）<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">青洲 91</span><br />\n大老山 78<br />\n橫瀾島 68<br />\n赤柱 66 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">天星碼頭 64 </span><br />\n長洲泳灘 62<br />\n長洲 *58<br />\n<br />\n青洲陣風更達暴風程度<br />\n維港天星陣風亦達烈風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a99f3d819c06a145ac57d6310ab45e4650b2cdc","tid":102820,"uid":36650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T01:16:35.000Z","msg":"【特別提示】⚠風勢強勁，請注意海上安全⚠<br />\n<br />\n受強烈偏東氣流影響，本港普遍吹強勁偏東風，本港部份水域更達烈風程度，青洲亦於凌晨一度錄得91kph的暴風程度陣風。🌬🌬<br />\n<br />\n由於風勢強勁，本港離岸風浪頗大🌊🌊，本台在此提醒各位應儘量遠離岸邊，及停止一切水上活動，進行海上作業的人士亦須特別留意海上安全。<br />\n<br />\n由於海上風浪大🌊🌊，高速渡輪可能會出現減速或短暫停航的情況。"},{"pid":"e30b4971fc6c0dc861aed70aef843879b56afbb9","tid":102820,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T09:14:39.000Z","msg":"強 烈 季 候 風 信 號&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n強 烈 季 候 風 信 號 在 下 午 4 時 45 分 取 消 。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n以 上 天 氣 稿 由 天 文 台 於 2017 年 02 月 07 日 16 時 45 分 發 出"},{"pid":"c7c4b19879da62d9d13043df22a17104b61330eb","tid":102820,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T03:37:56.000Z","msg":"星期五低溫再下調一度至11度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或有望打破今冬11.5度低溫紀錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af1dc1ec29c13cf144b031812233ec83a9fedeac","tid":102820,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T04:14:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>特別天氣提示</span><br />\n<br />\n一道冷鋒將於今晚橫過廣東沿岸地區。受到與其相關的強烈東北季候風影響，今晚本港氣溫開始顯著下降，明早天氣寒冷。市民外出時請帶備保暖衣物。 (08-02-2017 12:00)</strong>"},{"pid":"0445d2a44669065f33a87620fbdb2eaa2155c23e","tid":102820,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T04:19:10.000Z","msg":"由12年cdrom睇氣象台，今日終於入黎留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2f493055b58b04363cfec34aa2c469b02ebaee3","tid":102820,"uid":44630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T04:23:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>由12年cdrom睇氣象台，今日終於入黎留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n歡迎"},{"pid":"7255f6fa35dff58cebdd90fffee83920f421b611","tid":102820,"uid":36650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T04:51:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>由12年cdrom睇氣象台，今日終於入黎留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nWelcome <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5da0d66726bcd636fb2f81d0d2ed49390c44cb5d","tid":102820,"uid":36650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T05:47:38.000Z","msg":"【特別提示】冷風過境，注意保暖<br />\n各位巴絲打，一道冷鋒預計將於今日傍晚時份開始橫過本港，而隨後嘅強烈東北季候風將為我哋帶嚟久違嘅寒冷天氣，預料氣溫將於今晚顯著下降。本台在此提醒各位朋友:<br />\n1. 請特別留意家中年長或長期病患嘅親友(尤其係獨居嘅老人家)<br />\n2. 使用熱水爐/暖爐時應該保持室內空氣嘅流通<br />\n3. 各位司機大佬，開車前應特別留意有無小動物(主要係喵星人)躲於車底或引擎<br />\n<br />\n今晚至聽朝嘅天氣預測:<br />\n預料冷鋒將於今日傍晚時份開始橫過本港 , 傍晚時份可能受鋒面雨影響有一兩陣微雨，聽朝天氣漸轉天晴；風方面，下晝繼續吹東風，冷鋒過境後將轉吹北風，晚間風勢增強；聽朝氣溫將持續下降至12度左右，新界及高地氣溫將再低幾度，須留意風勢加上晚間嘅微雨或會令體感溫度比實際溫度更冷。"},{"pid":"e8823e598357da8c13fa5c692433a15a27ff65c6","tid":102820,"uid":15949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T07:36:12.000Z","msg":"羽絨岀動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40e71896f7b3c57a2982bfe7a3f9e563e5db24de","tid":102820,"uid